      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_1_00014"/><hi rend="latintype">Herrn Doc<unclear>tor</unclear> Rich. Beer Hofma<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>.</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb190427" type="place">I Wollzeile 15</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1893_AS_RBH_1_00015"/>Lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>wenn Sie eine intere<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ante <hi rend="latintype">Hypnose</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehn wollen,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eien Sie morgen <add place="below"><date>Do <c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date></add> um <time>11.15 Vormittg</time> auf der <rs ref="#pmb41" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Poliklinik</hi></rs>, <rs ref="#pmb311" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Mariannengasse</hi></rs>, Abthlg <rs ref="#pmb12695" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Schnitzler</hi></rs>. – Ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ag es auch dem <rs ref="#pmb12740" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Schwarzkopf</hi></rs>. – Niemandem mittheilen! –</p><closer>Herzlich Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
